repo_metadata.description: A self-contained cryptographic library for Python

advisories.title: PyCryptodome Integer overflow vulnerability
advisories.description: PyCryptodome before 3.6.6 has an integer overflow in the data_len variable in AESNI.c, related to the AESNI_encrypt and AESNI_decrypt functions, leading to the mishandling of messages shorter than 16 bytes.

advisories.title: PyCryptodome and pycryptodomex side-channel leakage for OAEP decryption
advisories.description: PyCryptodome and pycryptodomex before 3.19.1 allow side-channel leakage for OAEP decryption, exploitable for a Manger attack.
